Text.Value: What do you know about this weapon?
Looking... for Her weapon... the Absolute...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: Do not... fight her. Power... such power...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: What will your siblings do now?
Is there anything valuable around here?
The Absolute... the almighty goddess...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: Brynna... Andrick...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: *The corpse regards you lifelessly.*

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell_LeadIn

Text.Value: *The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

EditorData.AnimationTags: Corpse Jerks violently, not answering you (its killer)
EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell_LeadOut

Text.Value: Edowin... a True Soul... a Chosen...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: Who 'chose' you?
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*

EditorData.AnimationTags: Corpse shudders as magic leaves it
EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell_LeadOut

Text.Value: Crashed... from the sky... taken... by infidels...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: Who are you?
Sister... brother... my job... to protect them...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: *The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell_LeadOut

Text.Value: Leave.

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell_LeadOut

Text.Value: Find weapon... for Absolute...

EditorData.SFXTags: Speak with dead spell to match VFX -   FX_SpeakWithDead_Spell

Text.Value: What were you doing here?
What can you tell me about the Absolute?
Who are Brynna and Andrick?

Synopsis: True Soul Edowin has been killed by an owlbear. This is his corpse speaking. He is concerned about his siblings and still devoted to the Absolute.
